    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, break the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> into small pieces</p><p>Combine the <strong>beef mince</strong>, <strong>cheddar pieces </strong>and <strong>chopped basil</strong> in a large mixing bowl with a large pinch of both <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix well with clean hands to fully combine</p>",
